Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.52,0:26:46.02,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Queriendo perseguir la aventura{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.02,0:26:52.02,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Dare mo min'na uzu-uzu shite 'ru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.02,0:26:52.02,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡Todos están ansiosos por ir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.02,0:26:58.03,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Otona no furi shite akiramecha{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.02,0:26:58.03,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Si actúas como adulto y te rindes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.03,0:27:04.20,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Kiseki no nazo nado tokenai yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.03,0:27:04.20,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡Nunca descifrarás el misterio\ndel milagro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.20,0:27:15.31,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,10,, {\i1}Motto wairudo ni motto takumashiku
ikite goran{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.20,0:27:15.31,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Intenta vivir aún\N{\i0}\N{\i1}¡más salvaje y fuerte!{\i0}
